{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abb4be38b2","title":"致达赖喇嘛电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f6516078b","index":0,"year":1951,"month":10,"day":26,"articleId":"abb4be38b2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"fa39086857","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖喇嘛，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，当时是西藏地方宗教和政治领袖之一。1951年10月24日致电毛泽东，表示西藏地方政府及藏族僧俗人民，一致拥护关于和平解放西藏办法的协议，愿意积极协助人民解放军进藏部队，巩固国防，驱逐帝国主义势力出西藏，保护祖国领土主权的统一。"},{"id":"9e7ef70d95","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"和平解放西藏协议，即1951年5月23日在北京签订的《中央人民政府和西藏地方政府关于和平解放西藏办法的协议》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c690274da6","type":"title","text":"致达赖喇嘛电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2"},{"id":"fa39086857","type":"paragraph","text":"达赖喇嘛先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2"},{"id":"9e7ef70d95","type":"paragraph","text":"你于一九五一年十月二十四日的来电，已经收到了。我感谢你对实行和平解放西藏协议的努力，并致表心的祝贺","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2"},{"id":"d9a36a5286","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2"},{"id":"48b0142bcd","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2"}],"page":{"id":"470cdcbd98","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"abb4be38b2","start":44,"end":44}}}},"__N_SSG":true}